name: A girl scared of a suspension bridge
description:
Kazura Bridge exists in the unexplored region of Tokushima Prefecture in Japan.
Length 45m, width 2m, water surface 14m. It is made of A. arguta, which weighs about 6 tons. The trees at your feet and the width of the trees are wide and quite thrilling.
The sadness of the girl who wants to go to her parents is well expressed.
